survey_response.review_text: Very professional, friendly and compassionate has been Dr Deepa's approach towards every patient. Very efficient and effective in our every appointment. She has become the go to doctor to my entire joint family for every kind of dental treatment. I strongly recommend Dr Deepa to anyone.

Dr Deepadnya is very patients and explains the problem well before starting any procedure. She handles all her patients personally and never hurries or rushes through. The clinic is well maintained and has several visiting specialists for complex procedures.

First & for most Important point is *** ** **** ********* Dr. Deepa explains the patient so well that as patient you get the feeling that you are 200% at right place. 
Generally Any treatment related to tooth is very painful & Sensetive, but as a doctor her hand & work is so smooth. That you will not even realize the treatment is completed. 

Second most very Important thing I would like to emphasize on Hygiene level of Clinic. Is mantain extremely well. 

Dr.Deepa Asst. miss Chitra is also very cooperative. 

What more you can expect from one good Doctor. 

I will suggest Dr.Deepa definitely to those who is looking for Good Dentist.

Thank you,
Vijay Panchal

I've recently had an dental appointment and visited Dr. Deepa Helekar at her Floss & Gloss Dental Care clinic.

*** ***** ** ** ********* ******** 

She spends sufficient time to explain each & every procedure she was doing, she also explains all the pros and cons of the treatment, when I got my teeth cleaning Dr. Deepa was very much supportive. 

I would strongly recommend Dr. Deepa & Dr. Kavya as both of them are highly professional, caring *** **** ** ********* ******* **** **** **** *** *** **** ******* * **** **** *****
About Clinic - 
It was great!! Clinic is neat and clean, very well maintained, & well organized, also very much spacious.

It was hygienic and had a good environment. All Sterilized instruments are used to help maintain hygiene. 

Very flexible, easy to re-book the dental appointment when needed, easily accessible and comfortable clinic.

I am happy that I found this very well maintained *** ********* ****** **** *******

My tooth extraction procedure was very easy going... Although I was scared but Dr. Deepa made me relaxed and comfortable and was explaining each and every little things and also communicating with me to distract me from my fear...She was also very sweet and I am satisfied with my visit there..

The treatment was for my mother, for her upper teeth. Deepa explained the possible options with dentures, screws  and helped us choose that suited our requirements. She is always patient n explains well..
My mother is very happy with the output and she is keen to get the lower denture as well after 6 months of using the upper denture. 
I would highly recommend Deepa for all sorts of dental treatments ..
